def.threejs.three

Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • def.js.Object
      • def.threejs.three.Vector
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Vector2, Vector3, Vector4

    @Interface
public abstract class Vector
extends def.js.Object
    ( interface Vector<T> ) Abstract interface of Vector2, Vector3 and Vector4. Currently the members of Vector is NOT type safe because it accepts different typed vectors. Those definitions will be changed when TypeScript innovates Generics to be type safe.
